graph LR
    MLflowOp[MLflow Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    MLflowOp -->|platform| K8s[Kubernetes 1.11.3+]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    MLflowOp -.->|TLS certs| OpenShift[OpenShift 4.x]
    MLflowOp -.->|backend store| PostgreSQL[PostgreSQL 9.6+]
    MLflowOp -.->|artifact store| S3[S3-compatible Storage]
    MLflowOp -.->|ingress| GatewayAPI[Gateway API v1]
    MLflowOp -.->|metrics| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator v1]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    MLflowOp -->|uses| ServiceCA[service-ca-operator<br/>OpenShift]
    MLflowOp -->|creates| HTTPRoutes[Gateway HTTPRoutes<br/>ODH/OpenShift]
    MLflowOp -->|creates| ConsoleLinks[OpenShift Console<br/>ConsoleLink CRD]

    %% MLflow Instance Dependencies
    MLflowInstance[MLflow Instances] -->|auth| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>self_subject_access_review]
    MLflowInstance -.->|backend| PostgreSQL
    MLflowInstance -.->|artifacts| S3
    MLflowInstance -->|TLS| ServiceCA

    %% Operator creates instances
    MLflowOp -->|deploys| MLflowInstance

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI integration| MLflowOp
    Notebooks[Jupyter Notebooks] -.->|mlflow client| MLflowInstance
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|auto logging| MLflowInstance

    %% Container Images
    Registry[Container Registry<br/>quay.io] -->|provides images| MLflowOp
    Registry -->|provides images| MLflowInstance

    %% Helm Charts
    HelmCharts[Embedded Helm Charts<br/>helm.sh/helm/v3] -->|renders manifests| MLflowOp

    %% Styling
    style MLflowOp fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px
    style MLflowInstance fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    style K8s fill:#326ce5,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#326ce5,stroke:#333

    style OpenShift fill:#ee0000,stroke:#333
    style ServiceCA fill:#ee0000,stroke:#333
    style ConsoleLinks fill:#ee0000,stroke:#333

    style PostgreSQL fill:#336791,stroke:#333
    style S3 fill:#ff9900,stroke:#333
    style GatewayAPI fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style PrometheusOp fill:#e6522c,stroke:#333

    style HTTPRoutes fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Notebooks fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Pipelines fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333

    style Registry fill:#40b4e5,stroke:#333
    style HelmCharts fill:#0f1689,stroke:#333
